{"tid":661034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠退休生活首天 第一站行程去咗殯儀館","createTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T08:55:13.000Z","uid":36494,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6944f47a84b7d0dd8684d0a2b083e6b74d7a0429","tid":661034,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T07:57:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180511&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58178272\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180511%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58178272&d=cvraUpSWqjSd0pn6kM4YLtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=008057eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180511%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58178272&h=af42c1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180511&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58178272</a><br />\n<br />\n【超人退休】李嘉誠退休生活首天 第一站行程去咗殯儀館<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n約10時35分，李嘉誠的座駕到達北角殯儀館，有一男一女高層人員早在門口恭候，其中男的跟李嘉誠親切握手，女的則扶著李一同進入殯儀館內。約中午12時，李離開殯儀館，他指前來送別友好。他隨後登上座駕，返回長江中心。"},{"pid":"f21e8c7a06b629f3e9709b180be0d1e9ac357cbf","tid":661034,"uid":23734,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:00:05.000Z","msg":"馬英九看手錶.JPG"},{"pid":"f26eceadb95e154a3a676f17a0c9e858bcee75c4","tid":661034,"uid":16461,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/11/160121_ce7da413331f9dc3a8629e966b0817f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F11%2F160121_ce7da413331f9dc3a8629e966b0817f3.png&h=faad9183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccad96bf3dfe2f9d94d451d50e1edaef42489e7b","tid":661034,"uid":179283,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠退休首天 左腳先步出大門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207db0cf3335564